text: Atlantique is one of the twelve departments of Benin. Atlantique is divided into the communes of Abomey-Calavi, Allada, Kpomassè, Ouidah, Sô-Ava, Toffo, Tori-Bossito, and Zè. In 1999 the Littoral Department was split off from Atlantique. == References == Category:Departments of Benin
title: Atlantique Department
